  - default-deny triage
  - verification inversion
  - AI security
abstract: >-
  This paper proposes an architecture for LLM context management that
  separates commands and data into distinct memory spaces with default-deny
  triage. All incoming content enters the data tier by default and must pass
  through evaluation and summarisation gates before promotion to the command
  tier. The architecture addresses both prompt injection vulnerability and
  context degradation as consequences of the undifferentiated context window.
  Native Memory Paper 2.
